    &lt;dependencies&gt;
        &lt;dependency&gt;
            &lt;groupId&gt;org.projectlombok&lt;/groupId&gt;
            &lt;artifactId&gt;lombok&lt;/artifactId&gt;
            &lt;version&gt;1.18.22&lt;/version&gt;
            &lt;scope&gt;provided&lt;/scope&gt;
        &lt;/dependency&gt;
    &lt;/dependencies&gt;

This should be enough. 

